  <li>Life is a gift</li>
  <li>Life is temporary and everything in life is temporary, you can lose anything anytime</li> 
  <li>Life is gray, something terrible is not that bad and something good is not that good</li> 
  <li>Life has ups and downs and there are no good or bad events, we see after many years if it was really good or bad</li> 
  <li>Life has both light and darkness together</li>  
  <li>Life has no destination, enjoy the journey</li> 
  <li>I love myself so I practice self-love, self-care, gratitude, and forgiveness - Self-esteem - عزت نفس</li> 
  <li>I love life and appreciate it as a gift and live like a curious kid  - Enthusiasm  - شور و شوق</li> 
  <li>I accept what I cannot control and know there is no good or bad - Acceptance - پذیرش</li> 
  <li>I choose to live fearlessly by making decisions to change and improve what I can control - Bravery  - شهامت</li> 
  <li>I let it go and let it be, I go with the flow,  stay flexible with change and enjoy the experience - Flow - رها</li>
  <li>I grow by embracing Growth-Mindset and seeing life challenges as opportunities - Growth - رشد</li>
  <li>I practice hope and happiness every day - Hope - امید</li>
